00:36:23.960 --> 00:36:25.080
When you go to Black Tiger Mountain,

00:36:26.240 --> 00:36:27.560
You must be careful.

00:36:29.360 --> 00:36:30.280
I promise you.

00:36:54.800 --> 00:36:56.640
Son, what are you doing here?

00:36:57.840 --> 00:36:58.880
Why does that man surnamed Tian

00:36:59.200 --> 00:37:00.280
always come to our house?

00:37:00.360 --> 00:37:02.120
No, that Tian

00:37:02.520 --> 00:37:04.280
is a distant relative of our family.

00:37:04.560 --> 00:37:06.040
My family is in trouble.

00:37:06.040 --> 00:37:07.600
Come to our house for a while.

00:37:07.600 --> 00:37:09.120
Stop asking and go back to your room.

00:37:10.120 --> 00:37:12.000
He doesn't look like a good person.

00:37:12.000 --> 00:37:12.880
Shut up!

00:37:15.240 --> 00:37:16.560
If you keep talking nonsense,

00:37:16.800 --> 00:37:18.120
I'll send you back to your hometown.

00:37:18.280 --> 00:37:19.320
Go back to your room and study.

00:37:36.720 --> 00:37:37.760
Madam,

00:37:37.960 --> 00:37:39.440
Do you have anything else to say?

00:37:41.120 --> 00:37:42.440
Go to Black Tiger Mountain.

00:37:42.960 --> 00:37:44.640
No matter who you meet on the road,

00:37:44.840 --> 00:37:46.640
just do what I told you to do.

00:37:47.000 --> 00:37:47.760
Okay.

00:37:49.080 --> 00:37:50.320
You know what to do.

00:37:50.520 --> 00:37:51.280
Got it.

00:37:51.440 --> 00:37:52.560
Don’t worry.

00:37:53.680 --> 00:37:54.560
Get on the horse.

00:37:55.320 --> 00:37:56.280
Have a safe trip.

